msgstr "Pemberitahuan Admin"

#: inc/rpt-optin-form.php:457
msgid "Updates, Announcement, Marketing. No Spam, I promise."
msgstr "Pembaruan, Pengumuman, Pemasaran. Tanpa Spam, saya janji."

#: inc/rpt-optin-form.php:459
msgid "Plugin Actions"
msgstr "Tindakan Plugin"

#: inc/rpt-optin-form.php:460
msgid ""
"Active, Deactive, Uninstallation and How you use this plugin's features and "
"settings. This is limited to usage data. It does not include any of your "
"sensitive rpt data, such as traffic. This data helps us learn which "
"features are most popular, so we can improve the plugin further."
msgstr ""
"Aktif, Nonaktif, Penghapusan dan Cara Anda menggunakan fitur dan pengaturan "
"plugin ini. Ini terbatas pada data penggunaan. Ini tidak termasuk data rpt "
"sensitif Anda, seperti lalu lintas. Data ini membantu kami memahami fitur "
"mana yang paling populer, sehingga kami dapat meningkatkan plugin lebih "
"lanjut."

